data.description: One-level townhome living in Belle Plaine. This 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem boasts over 2600 finished square feet, offering an open main floor adorned with vaulted ceilings & hardwood floors. Relax in the warmth of the sunroom, complete with a gas fireplace. The spacious primary suite features a large walk-in closet & a generous sized bathroom with a separate tub/shower. Accompanying the main level is a 2nd bedroom, full bathroom, & convenient laundry room that leads out to the attached 2 car garage. The lower level has 9-foot ceilings & was just finished last year. It holds a family room, 2 additional bedrooms, & another 3/4 bathroom. Enjoy the charm of a front porch & unwind on the back patio. As a bonus, relish the proximity to a park just across the street. Relaxed & affordable association (only $50/month) & don’t worry about snow plowing or grass cutting anymore! Welcome to your new townhome haven!
